      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELEGANTLY WRITTEN (3) is a lightly raced mare having her first try at this trip. Up in grade but attractively weighted and looks hard to hold out. Hard to fault FLORENCE GLASS (2) who has been in sparkling form winning two on end. Ran on well to score this level last time and looks tough to stop again. TIDEFORD (7) comes through the race won by Quafftide and after drawing the outside gate was forced to burn early and had nothing left at the finish. Much better gate this time and with a softer lead will give a sight and can bounce back. HAPPY CLAN (1) was runner-up behind FLORENCE GLASS last time and could well turn the tables. GODDESS OF ROCK (4) was fifth in the same race. Rates highly on best form so she can turn things around.",
